        "rich_text_KfVgfM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Because of these advantages, CVD diamonds are increasingly becoming the preferred choice for luxury jewelry brands and conscious buyers.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, we use advanced CVD technology to ensure that every diamond shines with unmatched clarity and ethical confidence. Our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-for-women\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> engagement ring for women</span></a> and<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/couple-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> couple rings</span></a> are perfect examples of CVD diamonds crafted for modern elegance.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Identify a CVD Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Identify a CVD Diamond</h2><p>If you’re exploring the world of lab-grown diamonds, it’s important to know how to identify them correctly. Here’s what to look for:</p><ol><li>Certification: Always buy certified diamonds. Look for IGI or GIA reports that specify “CVD” as the growth method.<br/></li><li>Inclusions: CVD diamonds often have fewer inclusions than HPHT diamonds.<br/></li><li>Laser Inscription: Most certified CVD diamonds have a microscopic inscription on the girdle identifying them as lab-grown.<br/></li><li>Expert Guidance: When in doubt, consult Lucira’s gemologists or visit our Diamond Education section to learn more.<br/></li></ol><p>Understanding the CVD full form in diamond ensures that you make an informed, confident, and ethical choice when purchasing fine jewelry.</p>",
            "custom_id": "identify"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cHxj38": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Future of CVD Diamonds in India",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Future of CVD Diamonds in India</h2><p>India is emerging as a global leader in lab-grown diamond production and innovation. As sustainability becomes a lifestyle choice, CVD diamonds are reshaping how Indian consumers perceive luxury.</p><p>Millennials and Gen Z shoppers are embracing<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond rings</span></a> for their authenticity, transparency, and environmental responsibility. Lucira Jewelry, as one of India’s best lab-grown diamond brands, is at the forefront of this movement—bringing together craftsmanship, technology, and purpose.</p><p>Embrace the Brilliance of the Future</p><p>The CVD diamond full form—Chemical Vapor Deposition—represents more than a scientific process. It symbolizes a new era of brilliance that balances luxury with responsibility. Whether you’re celebrating love, milestones, or personal success,<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond jewellery</span></a> allows you to shine with both style and conscience.</p><p>Ready to experience brilliance with purpose? Explore Lucira’s ethically crafted CVD diamond jewelry, where innovation meets elegance. Every piece tells a story of modern craftsmanship and conscious beauty.</p>",
            "custom_id": "future"
          }
        }
